<br>
It's great how the Australians airlifting people to burn centres for medical attention. I think they have a good government there, but then we never really hear about its faults.<br>
<br>
Are the dead getting ignored and used as a show of what terrorism does? Or is this simple what Bush warned of?<br>
<br>
